                                         CAPE TOWN - A 38-year old man has been shot dead at the Bellville  Taxi Rank after a confrontation between taxi drivers and a traffic officer. According to reports, traffic officers failed to pull over a taxi driver along Voortrekker Road and gave chase. Police say they ended up at the Bellville Taxi Rank, where a crowd stormed towards the traffic officers. Police say shots were fired and one man was killed, while another was wounded.